Once upon a time I fulfilled my life goal of jump roping at the @sweetsweat booth at a fitness expo ✨ I jumped for a total of 60 minutes straight and I did it with joy 🥹 

.
Legit one  of the best moments of my life 🥹 talk about making dreams a reality. I was on my way down from 187lbs at 165 felt self conscious In a sport bra and didn’t have the condition to do this.. but when I got the call for the job I didn’t even hesitate.… I filled in  for one of their conditioned jumpers who was out sick .. if at any point you’re given an opportunity for a job and you have no idea how or if you can do it . Take it and figure out the rest later 😂😜Sink or swim baby and then you really find what you’re made of 🥹✨
.

Recap on my trip to Vegas for worlds ✨
.
In no particular order: 
.
I cancelled my flight last min and ended up arriving a day later than I planned because i was waiting on a gown and ended up having way too much stuff to take .It was a long 6 hour drive on 3 hours of sleep but nothing a bang drink can’t help you through 
.
The sketchiest part of my drive was when my phone lost connection and I lost navigation on the Mercedes connect app. . I missed my exit and ended up cruising through a city I had never heard of 🫣I saw they had the world famous jerky and was tempted to stop but I feel like this is how women are kidnapped so I didn’t.  Word of advice: just pay the $600 for the built in navigation sis 😂😩

* I got to spend time with my favorite @aliciagowans_wbffpro @xkyrgios @allysangelscoaching team and baby georgie 🥺 & tried to convince Alicia to have her baby a day early so we can share birthdays 🫣
.
@barbell.blondie pulled me out of the cave and took me to Bellagio to eat steak and see the garden 🥺 thank you Audra that was the first decent meal I had in over a few weeks 🫣 she also brought me coffee every day 🥺
.
My Jessie @jess.fit2  was my partner in crime for the weekend 🫣 thank you Jess couldn’t have done it without you
.
I invited every single one of my clients for fittings to ensure everyone looked and felt like. Billion bucks 
.
I watched @growwithgab_x on stage and off stage in action and I protected @toby.harrison  life while he laid on the road and risked it all to get a shot 
.
I got to see my beautiful @melissa_wbffpro and her husband who brought me idk how many drinks so I could chill out and watch the show 🫣 
.
I had the best time watching all of my friends and clients shine on stage 🥺 ✨
.
I also got to catch up with my tall supermodel babe @miss.rasheenafit ❤️ and my gorgeous @freda8655 
.
& made a mess in the room ..all of which I threw in my luggage and said I’ll deal with this later .. haven’t dealt with it yet 😂🫣
.
I’ve spent the last week in bed dealing with sickness 🫣
.
But despite everything I had a blast ❤️ thank you to everyone for the wonderful memories ✌️ 
.
@xmplary_bikinis ✨
.

For a brief moment I thought I was done. I thought I had lost it all. My life blew up right before my eyes and as events unfolded I had to watch everything crumble. I felt helpless. There was nothing I could do except endure the storm, not knowing how long it would last or how much more damage it would cause …I held on to whatever i could… until I finally had to let go. And as I went through the most trying time of my life I finally broke. Life as I knew it had changed. I had no choice but to face my new reality… So I picked up the pieces …and this was the result ✨
.
.
I am Eternally grateful for every single soul that allowed me a safe space to completely dismantle, a safe space to heal, but most importantly; a safe space to grow and to continue expressing my creativity
.
 I will never be able to put into words how much the support meant to me ❤️

.
I’m not sure what tomorrow will hold but I am happy to be here ❤️
.
.
Closing out the work year with so much love and appreciation ❤️ THANK YOU 
.
